{"tid":2302073,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"沙特阿拉伯王儲出資收購SNK 33%股權 取代支那成為SNK最大股東","createTime":"2020-11-27T00:19:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-27T06:47:13.000Z","uid":22675,"like":18,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"cad0122766c6cd4eaed9aefd7d87ae330e1ad846","tid":2302073,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T00:19:37.000Z","msg":"據韓國媒體Bloter報導，沙特遊戲開發公司EGDC今日收購了SNK 33%的股份，成為其最大的股份持有者。這筆投資由沙特王儲穆罕默德&middot;本&middot;薩勒曼全資資助，預計將在明年一月完成。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n這或許是王儲主導的「沙特2030」計劃的組成部分，旨在使石油產業為主導的沙特實現經濟多樣化，他本人也是SNK遊戲的粉絲。SNK旗下擁有《拳皇》《合金彈頭》《侍魂》等經典遊戲系列，目前第二大股東為持股18%的完美世界，本次收購也會涉及這部分股權。"},{"pid":"e0d99ec88aebcd4066fdcee5e5f239526b532297","tid":2302073,"uid":264121,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T00:22:00.000Z","msg":"gd news"},{"pid":"eba38cdff2deec03d090d4e53a9c949fd3185f70","tid":2302073,"uid":144001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T01:36:15.000Z","msg":"可以搞幾大都得 metal slug用unreal engine<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd3f8b6eaa2d9aef2066173d41bf98c0753d23e8","tid":2302073,"uid":30464,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T01:43:02.000Z","msg":"越南大戰是咪再無阿拉伯人同騎駱陀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb537c0053437f58353a7c3e5cf3f1acd9f68ba0","tid":2302073,"uid":169195,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T01:46:07.000Z","msg":"明明<br />\nMetal Slug d 畫風好正<br />\nKOF 97, 月華，侍魂，D人設好正<br />\n<br />\n點解成日易手 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be49e98142946d8ed41c2cde975242088f241805","tid":2302073,"uid":34523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bd3f8b6eaa2d9aef2066173d41bf98c0753d23e8","tid":2302073,"uid":30464,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTim